## Data Attribution

This project uses data from NASA FIRMS (Fire Information for Resource Management System):
- Data Source: NASA MODIS/VIIRS Fire Detection
- API: FIRMS Web Services
- Terms: https://earthdata.nasa.gov/earth-observation-data/data-use-policy

Users must comply with NASA's data use policies when using this software.

